'''Ghafla!''' is an entertainment news [[website]] that was started in 2011.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.humanipo.com/news/34/ghafla-found-new-team-members-and-a-surprise-investment-through-ipo48-platform/ |title=Ghafla! found new team-members and a surprise investment through IPO48 platform |date= |accessdate= |website=HumanIPO |publisher= |last= |first= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150718055544/http://www.humanipo.com/news/34/ghafla-found-new-team-members-and-a-surprise-investment-through-ipo48-platform/ |archivedate=2015-07-18 |df= }}</ref>
