'''HD NVD''' Is a Chinese [[High-definition video|High definition]] standard created to compete with [[Blu-ray]] discs. The standard uses a red laser like the one used in [[DVD]] and [[CD]] players whereas Blu-ray uses a [[blue laser]]. This standard allows the Chinese companies to avoid paying royalties to foreign companies for the manufacture of Blu-ray products.

